86
00:05:15,363 --> 00:05:23,769
And those individual councils, one of their required, well, one of their tasks as a school council is to draft changes to the handbook.

87
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:31,034
And they get a pretty big, October 1st to January 31st is the expected time when they would do that work.

88
00:05:32,094 --> 00:05:37,238
And then finally, this comes back to the school committee for approval sometime between February 1st and April 30th.

89
00:05:38,479 --> 00:05:51,611
